          ></span>
        </a>
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex justify-center items-center mx-auto relative w-full h-auto"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <div class="flex flew-row gap-6 md:gap-8 justify-center items-center title">
          <div
            class="relative w-full flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-1 md:gap-8"
          >
            <h1 class="text-black text-8xl md:text-[8rem] font-compactaBT">
